Author :: Charles Gretton 2009

-------- PCogX-alpha^2 -----------------------------
----------------------------------------------------
----------------------------------------------------

These are the release notes for PCogX-alpha^2.  Read them carefully,
as they tell you what this is all about, explain how to install
PCogX-alpha^2, and what to do if something goes wrong.


WHAT IS PCogX-alpha^2?
----------------------

Executive :: This is a decision-theoretic planning
subsystem/subarchitecture that is intended for use in cognitive
systems that self-understand and self-extend. The development of this
library was wholly supported (financially and emotionally) by by EC
FP7-IST grant 215181-CogX (see \url{http://cogx.eu/}).

HOW CAN I CONTACT THE AUTHORS?
------------------------------

You can email _Charles Gretton_ at :: charles.gretton@gmail.com
You can email _Richard Dearden_ at :: R.W.Dearden@cs.bham.ac.uk

